  <brief_title>Kirschner Wire and Pull-out Wire Fixation for the Treatment of Bony Mallet Finger</brief_title>
  <official_title>Kirschner Wire and Pull-out Wire Fixation for the Treatment of Bony Mallet Finger</official_title>
